description: This hall of fame Plezier purrs with a rating of 39, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 312, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and 1 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [312 Votes, Hall of Fame]
